channel.title: AUXYQUEST - E/E (James Lucien) [Meme, Parody]
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/eslashe/auxyquest
The greatest day of Henrik Lenberg's life.
Parody of Brodyquest by Neil Cicierega, the beautiful masterpiece can be found [here](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ygI-2F8ApUM).
Featuring ME on vocals! Damn, it sounds terrible xD but I tried. I wanted it to be full out Auxy. All tones are from the Auxy app, except for my voice. I realize now that I was butchering the pronunciation but give me a break it was 2 am when I recorded it x3
![auxyquest|500x500](upload://yi3KPIY5ZNAc2emu5nIDOuTQlOX.jpg)
